<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV19">
<l>kārikai yārniṟai kāppavar yāreṉṟu kārkoṇṭiṉṉē</l>
<l>mārikai yēṟi yaṟaiyiṭuṅ kālattum vāḻiyarō</l>
<l>cārikaip puḷḷaran taṇṇan tuḻāyiṟai kūyaruḷār</l>
<l>cērikai yēṟum paḻiyāy viḷaintateṉ ciṉmoḻikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Women, who will guard [their] plumpness”, in the time too when</l>
<l>cloud hands rise with rain now [and] deliver blows, may they live.</l>
<l>He on the coursing bird did not grace [me] with plucking a piece of [his] pretty cool Tulsi.</l>
<l>It ripened into blame that comes to hand in the quarter, for my [girl of] few words.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
